        "subject": "LU-11327 mdd: do not link file to PENDING on migrate",
        "message": "LU-11327 mdd: do not link file to PENDING on migrate\n\nmigrate does not apply for open objects. Then if an object is linked\nto PENDING directory, there will be no way to unlink it from there\nbecause there will be no close.\n\nDo not link objects to PENDING on migrate.\n\nTest illustrating the issue is added.\n\nCray-bug-id: LUS-6319\nSigned-off-by: Vladimir Saveliev <c17830@cray.com>\nChange-Id: Ibb9d43e9456879722d095ed5a608898d0242c599\n"
